msgstr "It never occurs to them:"

msgctxt "mn55:8-10.11"
msgid ""
"‘sādhu vata māyaṃ gahapati vā gahapatiputto vā paṇītena piṇḍapātena "
"pariviseyyāti."
msgstr "‘It’s so good that this householder serves me with delicious alms-food!"

