"drawback, and understanding the escape."

msgctxt "mn55:8-10.15"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, jīvaka, "
msgstr "What do you think, Jīvaka? "

msgctxt "mn55:8-10.16"
msgid ""
"api nu so bhikkhu tasmiṃ samaye attabyābādhāya vā ceteti, parabyābādhāya vā "
"ceteti, ubhayabyābādhāya vā cetetī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"At that time is that mendicant intending to hurt themselves, hurt others, or "
"hurt both?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "mn55:8-10.17"
msgid "“No hetaṃ, bhante”."
msgstr "“No, sir.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "mn55:8-10.18"
msgid ""
"“Nanu so, jīvaka, bhikkhu tasmiṃ samaye anavajjaṃyeva āhāraṃ āhāretī”ti?"
msgstr "“Aren’t they eating blameless food at that time?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya11"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi1.371"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "mn55:11.1"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante."
msgstr "“Yes, sir."

msgctxt "mn55:11.2"
msgid "Sutaṃ metaṃ, bhante:"
msgstr "Sir, I have heard that"

msgctxt "mn55:11.3"
msgid "‘brahmā upekkhāvihārī’ti."
msgstr "Brahmā abides in equanimity."

msgctxt "mn55:11.4"
msgid "Taṃ me idaṃ, bhante, bhagavā sakkhidiṭṭho;"
msgstr "Now, I’ve seen the Buddha with my own eyes,"

msgctxt "mn55:11.5"
msgid "bhagavā hi, bhante, upekkhāvihārī”ti."
msgstr "and it is the Buddha who truly abides in equanimity.”"

msgctxt "mn55:11.6"
msgid ""
"“Yena kho, jīvaka, rāgena yena dosena yena mohena vihesavā assa arativā assa "
"paṭighavā assa so rāgo so doso so moho tathāgatassa pahīno ucchinnamūlo "
"tālāvatthukato anabhāvaṅkato āyatiṃ anuppādadhammo."
msgstr ""
"“Any greed, hate, or delusion that might give rise to cruelty, negativity, "
"or repulsion has been given up by the Realized One, cut off at the root, "
"made like a palm stump, obliterated, and is unable to arise in the future."

msgctxt "mn55:11.7"
msgid "Sace kho te, jīvaka, idaṃ sandhāya bhāsitaṃ, anujānāmi te etan”ti."
msgstr "If that’s what you were referring to, I acknowledge it.”"

msgctxt "mn55:11.8"
msgid "“Etadeva kho pana me, bhante, sandhāya bhāsitaṃ”."
msgstr "“That’s exactly what I was referring to.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya12"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "mn55:12.1"
msgid ""
"“Yo kho, jīvaka, tathāgataṃ vā tathāgatasāvakaṃ vā uddissa pāṇaṃ ārabhati so "
"pañcahi ṭhānehi bahuṃ apuññaṃ pasavati."
msgstr ""
"“Jīvaka, anyone who slaughters a living creature specially for the Realized "
"One or the Realized One’s disciple makes much bad karma for five reasons."

msgctxt "mn55:12.2"
msgid "Yampi so, gahapati, evamāha:"
msgstr "When they say:"

msgctxt "mn55:12.3"
msgid ""
"‘gacchatha, amukaṃ nāma pāṇaṃ ānethā’ti, iminā paṭhamena ṭhānena bahuṃ "
"apuññaṃ pasavati."
msgstr "‘Go, fetch that living creature,’ this is the first reason."

msgctxt "mn55:12.4"
msgid ""
"Yampi so pāṇo galappaveṭhakena ānīyamāno dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti, "
"iminā dutiyena ṭhānena bahuṃ apuññaṃ pasavati."
msgstr ""
"When that living creature experiences pain and sadness as it’s led along by "
"a collar, this is the second reason."

msgctxt "mn55:12.5"
msgid "Yampi so evamāha:"
msgstr "When they say:"

msgctxt "mn55:12.6"
msgid ""
"‘gacchatha imaṃ pāṇaṃ ārabhathā’ti, iminā tatiyena ṭhānena bahuṃ apuññaṃ "
"pasavati."
msgstr "‘Go, slaughter that living creature,’ this is the third reason."

msgctxt "mn55:12.7"
msgid ""
"Yampi so pāṇo ārabhiyamāno dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti, iminā "
"catutthena ṭhānena bahuṃ apuññaṃ pasavati."
msgstr ""
"When that living creature experiences pain and sadness as it’s being "
"slaughtered, this is the fourth reason."

msgctxt "mn55:12.8"
msgid ""
"Yampi so tathāgataṃ vā tathāgatasāvakaṃ vā akappiyena āsādeti, iminā "
"pañcamena ṭhānena bahuṃ apuññaṃ pasavati."
msgstr ""
"When they provide the Realized One or the Realized One’s disciple with "
"unallowable food, this is the fifth reason."

msgctxt "mn55:12.9"
msgid ""
"Yo kho, jīvaka, tathāgataṃ vā tathāgatasāvakaṃ vā uddissa pāṇaṃ ārabhati so "
"imehi pañcahi ṭhānehi bahuṃ apuññaṃ pasavatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"Anyone who slaughters a living creature specially for the Realized One or "
"the Realized One’s disciple makes much bad karma for five reasons.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya13"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "mn55:13.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, jīvako komārabhacco bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "When he had spoken, Jīvaka said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "mn55:13.2"
msgid "“acchariyaṃ, bhante, abbhutaṃ, bhante."
msgstr "“It’s incredible, sir, it’s amazing!"

msgctxt "mn55:13.3"
msgid "Kappiyaṃ vata, bhante, bhikkhū āhāraṃ āhārenti;"
msgstr "The mendicants indeed eat allowable food."

msgctxt "mn55:13.4"
msgid "anavajjaṃ vata, bhante, bhikkhū āhāraṃ āhārenti."
msgstr "The mendicants indeed eat blameless food."

msgctxt "mn55:13.5"
msgid "Abhikkantaṃ, bhante, abhikkantaṃ, bhante … pe …"
msgstr "Excellent, sir! Excellent! …"

msgctxt "mn55:13.6"
msgid "upāsakaṃ maṃ bhagavā dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan”ti."
msgstr ""
"From this day forth, may the Buddha remember me as a lay follower who has "
"gone for refuge for life.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "mn55:13.7"
msgid "Jīvakasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
